<ContentSection title="Introduction" id="intro">
  <Fragment slot="lead">
    Clare College Tennis Club is a relaxed and welcoming environment for both beginners and more-experienced players to come and play tennis.
    <br />
    <br />
    <img src="https://humankinetics.me/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/federer-australian-open-2016-quarters_2.jpg" 
    width="400"
    class="center"/>
    <br />
    <br />
    Clare boasts 2 hard courts as well as 6 well-maintained grass courts (available for use in summer) located at the Clare sports ground. These are free to use by all members of the college. 
    <br />
    <br />
    <img src="https://www.middlesexasphaltservicesinc.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/tenniscourts-middlesexasphaltservices.jpg" 
    width="400"
    class="center"/>
    <br />
    <br />    
    Compete in weekly matches or practice with friends, theres something at clare tennis for everyone!
